commit.message: Add MSB validation to raise when timestamp overflows 128 bits

Add API create method and min/max random consts

This should allow easier creation of ULID values from fixed timestamps
for range queries, e.g.:

timestamp = time.time()
value = ulid.create(timestamp, ulid.MAX_RANDOM)

Freeze isort to 4.x on py36

Revert when https://github.com/timothycrosley/isort/issues/1273 is merged
Add support for bin, oct, and hex representations
Pin isort to 4.x version for py35

Add pickle support to MemoryView

With pickle support, these instances now support copy.copy
and copy.deepcopy.
Fix pytest warning about fixture positional args

Explicitly define public api in __init__.py

This is required because mypy --strict uses --no-implicit-reexport.
See: https://github.com/python/mypy/issues/7423
